description: This file is a React functional component for a Confluence Spaces page UI, allowing users to search and create Confluence spaces via API calls.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Asynchronously calls the 'search_spaces' tool with provided tenant, connector, and query parameters; updates UI state based on results or errors.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Asynchronously calls the 'create_space' tool with tenant, connector, and query as the space name; updates UI with the result or error.
